{"tid":2372569,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"研究：新冠重症痊癒者 八分之一會在5個月內死亡","createTime":"2021-01-19T19:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T22:21:57.000Z","uid":13468,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7d61db45c7ecc9acaab835c901517bcda6ec12e9","tid":2372569,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T19:14:35.000Z","msg":"英國每日電訊報報導，英國萊斯特大學與英國國家統計局的研究顯示，新冠肺炎重症痊癒者中，近三分之一會在五個月內再度就醫，八分之一會在五個月內死亡。<br />\n<br />\n這分研究顯示，新冠重症患者痊癒後，其中許多人出現心臟問題、糖尿病和慢性肝腎問題。<br />\n<br />\n在第一波出院的4萬7780名新冠病患中，29.4%在140天內再度就醫，總人數的12.3%在140天內死亡。<br />\n<br />\n論文作者萊斯特大學基礎醫療、糖尿病和血管學教授昆提說：「這是針對出院新冠病患最大規模的研究，看來這些人回家之後，會受到新冠肺炎的長期影響，回院就醫甚至死亡。近30%再度就醫，人數很多。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120944/5183902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120944%2F5183902&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmepFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=bc26c796\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120944/5183902</a>"},{"pid":"fe72d4a5b8292ada6cb36677efddf14cf9d0cdf1","tid":2372569,"uid":383344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T19:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4913c3d69fc33b8ffd518cf52632f9c43f1591b0","tid":2372569,"uid":85461,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T19:38:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>英國研究</strong>"},{"pid":"c17027bf73c44522adc4ceff7625c49133781438","tid":2372569,"uid":116466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4913c3d69fc33b8ffd518cf52632f9c43f1591b0","tid":2372569,"uid":85461,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T19:38:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>英國研究</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T19:39:09.000Z","msg":"今次不得不信了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMolamola"},{"pid":"449266fd2f86b940e524e9571c94e4d35916e78d","tid":2372569,"uid":33336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T20:01:26